name: CreateWarehouseSavedQuery
description:
Create a new warehouse saved query.

Use this tool to create a new warehouse saved query within a specified environment. It facilitates the management of warehouse tables, allowing for efficient data handling and retrieval.

parameters.name: project_id
parameters.description: The ID of the project to access. Retrieve it via a call to /api/projects/.

value_schema.description: Project ID of the project you're trying to access. To find the ID of the project, make a call to /api/projects/.

parameters.name: warehouse_query_details
parameters.description: JSON object containing details for the warehouse saved query like 'id', 'name', 'query', 'status', 'created_by', 'created_at', 'sync_frequency', and more.
